descript.abstract: This line data layer represents roads for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Dane_MPO_Roads_2014.gdb, These road centerlines are published by the City of Madison-Metropolitan Planning Organization (MPO) and may differ from the roads data published by the Dane County Land Information Office.
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
descript.supplinf: For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement where applicable.
